Class CountedSchedule

  • java.lang.Object
    • ome.smuggler.core.types.Schedule<PositiveN>
      • ome.smuggler.core.msg.CountedSchedule

  • public class CountedSchedule
extends Schedule<PositiveN>
    Channel metadata to request the scheduling of a message and the sending of a counter to indicate how many times the message has been scheduled for delivery.
